---
title: Cal Smart Pineapple Turkey Bowls with DIY Salsa and  Veggie-Lime Rice
description: This bold turkey bowl is low on calories, but big on flavour. Stir it all together to enjoy everything at once. Sweet and juicy pineapple makes each bite pop!

